s Raj was not most responsive on messaging. But he got all the work done in time so that's what matters.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sreejita Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHuqQzbtcx2H8a-UVstsVbvi5erIc617SEMW18AnZ866hFXA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I reached out to NVS Electric for their services to put up a couple of light fixtures in my home. Raj came to my house to review the work needed. He explained to us the work that he would do and gave us a quote. His quote was the most reasonable out of all the others we had received, so we decided to engage his services, and he arrived with his team 3 days later. The team quickly put up the smaller light fixtures around the house. Raj patiently explained to us what they were doing and guided us to make the right decisions for ourselves. The fixture in the foyer was the most complicated, and it took multiple hours to put up. The team did an excellent job with all the lights. He went above and beyond in helping us identify what kind of switch to use and where to put it. Raj ensured that every light fixture was put up in the correct way. They worked for almost 10 hours straight, with only a few short breaks, and ensured that the job was done to our satisfaction. He is excellent at his craft. Both my husband and I are impressed by his knowledge and skills and his work ethic. We highly recommend him and will definitely engage his services in the future.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3RH2H-qzzz89i4kG7lp_U6n3hvT7e5naCajqBKUrEiA9jAQON_VfKj-7tdGcH3DhDXxa7ghQ8FIm7VbaCLGrXb6kNXhaMrn51_s_wPO2hOjvUcbTn7bohADuUjmqdo8oSl5v5G=k-no"],"When":"2025-4-23"},{"Name":"Ammar Haleem","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnVerweos4DOm-9FSe7Q3OQDexqNOVbJsVad0sfBWtxc5K3So=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience working with Raj. His pricing is fair and transparent, with no hidden surprises. He was flexible with the scope of work and made sure everything was done to satisfaction. Extremely knowledgeable and offered good faith guidance. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chan S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlsRwDOT1NyHQBP2gOfzQGxTd0tyidwTpP2tEd7YIzlmZuWrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exceptional service and craftsmanship from NVS Electric, LLC! Navraj, the owner and master electrician, exceeded our expectations in every way. His team's attention to detail and expertise were evident throughout the entire process, from rough-ins to trim and final installations. The end result is truly breathtaking - the luxurious chandeliers and landscaping lighting have elevated our high-end home to a whole new level. Navraj's professionalism, communication, and dedication to his craft are top-notch. If you're looking for an electrician who can handle complex, high-scale projects with precision and flair, look no further than NVS Electric, LLC. 5 stars and highly recommended!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn24rNRdghYARv2thvMkudiqsuK06RM8r4Rdwg7D3n1rLF5roedxmcOW65wZ9maTb9LWuGl2P1QET5Z-gxDUpgtN2f_IMZn9Mak-JozFNbSXozSrlGwSL10Gw-w3O25NyYp2aNafmg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn21v3AfgFMZdF1Ba7a0hrDzJJdyKLzATcpQ-3TNS6QylEnoZ6fqsW4GE1Wb7gAlAPCndAKIlqTz9WQjAg87Q2g-JoUdTAhHyJnQegEdJcQ8cyWDzxcabkt9q-5ooL1wJLbYr5fT=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3s8vjCOSHxVElX6IXuFgvqInbo03XYgizizRPehh9jCd7Wt374B3U1XVPjK4jelsUvdCg2SkvuS51hDYYAZyAGTm2AB12XlvFsgIKiJfRp_QeuqVkQcseVfCBOcFV4v0UMySqn=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0pyjslkEiJ3EuZDdbXQVqk0nRlTg8hFOs9Vg0TVL7tWwXBCRN8GmTsaeXnfpj90hsni1Z5fsJyVWvNM2Ut1rtpzR4ZZh6q56tuMGaWGXXqYOzJaMQVU0uaVajKQl9baO9wYuHU=k-no"],"When":"2024-4-22"},{"Name":"Nithin Angri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnXElYkj5qRDyJj1CKnw2MAAwq32Psw-nBoax27RCO4ygI241k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Ratin