rical work and will definitely use them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Muhammad Rahman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZts5P0s96l9bWg2vXRuONmOph6qH7sTFk4QtZplSIVPhLCw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had AFCI siemens breaker that was intermittently tripping, amber  arc fault light coming on. I  called Galaxy Electric.Roger came out and did through analysis.  Checked my outlet connection and checked my electrical panel. He found the issue.  He was very professional,  friendly and expert in his work.  He knew right away, it was faulty breaker, and changed it for me. I would highly recommend Galaxy Electric for all Electric needs, as they know what they're doing, and don't try to over sell, or press you to do something you don't need. Galaxy Electric is my go to company for all my Electric needs. Thank you Roger for great expert and professional work. Nice to see professional and very friendly people with reasonable price at Galaxy Electric.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"kevin J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ0cHpalyXw9R-040oFfGkwBzte_Me0IbRLmRVeCkKfLYLvvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Galaxy Electric replaced our electric panel and several GFCI outlets.  The owners and technicians are professional, knowledgable, and responsive to our request and inquiries.  They did a great job and we will work with them again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0zICnc-__soLPbbuHZ0rA_8kPKt4qDLxANS7xjUHKJuONZb4e6W-Vs0p1UXjhMLYJ3fsL6IF4hbXV95h99aVqDGnQigYR9A_SaxXXJpzYPQq5lkiUXBfoVUEb90S9UYMdDutGi6jnOh3DA=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-7"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
