s and switches for me last year. The work completed by Adam was so great I hired them again this week. One more thermostat needed to be replaced and Sean efficiently got that completed this morning. I highly recommend this company to everyone needing a reliable and cost effective electrician.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joanna Ducharme","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnzJK26d1rCKmW25cBQ_Q9DknpwpFYTUCuhBx35Og9KzstPw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wire Craft was awesome! Sean was very kind, considerate, and efficient. I would have him back anytime I had any other electrical needs or problems. They had fair flat rate pricing and most of all Sean was informative, transparent, and trustworthy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Linda Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHkUshx_9wHFquZ11nRIqGpPSJjSljGB-9bTts8Mc4-e0m7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our family has relied on Wire Craft with great results over years. Most recently we've worked with Sean to update/replace old smoke detectors and to troubleshoot and replace heater thermostat. While I'm sure they are busy I was impressed  that Sean took the time to explain things to me.  Wire Craft were at all times friendly, professional, and right on time!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Hau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTKNHvtmsgpz5isruxndBCVOhKCXLUG6XFZXKmR7SXPo352NQ0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I submitted a request to Wire Craft and was pleasantly surprised when they came out the very next day. I wasn’t expecting everything to be finished in one visit, but Sean got it all done: installing new smoke detectors with updated wiring, replacing an old thermostat, and fixing a broken light switch.\n\nEverything was completed quickly and efficiently. Sean was also extremely friendly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJDbNEi7KYUmDkZmIikoioNEwfor01YW3sZMFzWmaaOr-chg13=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have hired Wire Craft for at least four jobs in the past three years and I continue to come back. Their clear pricing, availability, and attention to detail is outstanding.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Donna Stewart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJcNFL-6cy_YTczhpu5eGYDNUCxNZx44iRbW0Qhs8vZHTNCA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love all the guys at Wirecraft. Company is quick to respond. They have added car charger installation, fixed breakers and added new wiring. Highly recommend using them for all your needs..","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
