c76fUqS9sJBA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have an older home, built in 1961, and virtually all of the plugins and switches were original equipment. This has led to all manner of electrical problems as well as fire hazards, so we needed to have every plug and switch throughout the house replaced with modern equivalents. Keifer, the owner of Ohana Electric, came out and did an extremely professional inspection and gave us an honest evaluation and estimate. He and his crew did a masterful job of installing and testing to make certain that everything was done properly. All of them were both personable and professional at all times and we were extremely happy with both their work and clean up. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Walker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLIBfd2b8sryYTwq0-2m8viLOm8xgTzK1r2k6MB2o00kX91PhQFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t say enough good things about Ohana Electric! From the very first call, their friendliness and professionalism stood out—they truly make you feel like part of their ohana (family). Their pricing was not only reasonable but also very competitive compared to other quotes I received, and I never once felt like they were upselling or cutting corners.\n\nThe quality of their work speaks for itself—everything was done efficiently, neatly, and to the highest standard. They took the time to explain what they were doing, answered all my questions patiently, and left the space cleaner than they found it.\n\nIt’s rare to find a contractor who combines this level of customer care, fair pricing, and top-notch craftsmanship. I wouldn’t hesitate to recommend Ohana Electric to anyone in need of electrical work. They’ve definitely earned my trust and future business!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Wo1dFbV444UGmHjFtjl4alQDDkwtzv6BM-aWls87nKzO9Aqt7hrX-5E4YZOQ3eMgUEIAN4KYiXgeN2WnjGazeyuWyjDth7Ow9FW5_2Mft_VnkNLXq8vK6p