ion":"Steve responded super quickly and was very upfront with advice even before booking their service. Patrick was able to come out the next day and fix an overheating breaker for us. Both were exceptionally friendly, communicative, and professional. They will definitely be my first call going forward!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Isaacson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKOHVi7Od77FiYWzqNUNeMfYaTgiHyk55n3b6cqbDNnzTs7A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely phenomenal work.\nI’ve had them do two larger projects.\nBring a 60amp circuit from one side of the house to another(was a very difficult project). Hook up multiple new things(sauna, cold plunge, heater w timer under covered porch), fix some older things like heated floor panel, outside outlets, and add an additional outlet to pantry.\nThey were on time, clean, and efficient.\n\nThanks gents!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jana Koeberle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCne1xFAnORLu9CcbhV2hNLkmAR3qQIqhZr_5xUhNanbPvXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hired Streamline to install 3 room fans with the remotes attached at the wall, running electrical up through the attic, as well as to install an exterior outlet at the back of my home. Don and Christian were timely, professional, very friendly, and worked out just what to do and how to do it. They left everything as clean as it was to begin with. I would absolutely hire them again and recommend them to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Josh Breiling","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMTTt02b7zt-DLAWnOXfZ4Kj_dycOvJ6vYsmuFIJS84Rfsihoi=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Many thanks to the Streamline team for helping us last week with our multi-day project: installing over a dozen new ceiling lights across two rooms with a new three-way switch circuit, replacing numerous light fixtures across four rooms, upgrading a 240v receptacle to current code, running a new circuit for an appliance, and troubleshooting/improving far-less-than-ideal existing circuitry that was discovered (grounds as neutrals, no grounds at all, weird circuit pathways had some receptacles/lights on inappropriate breakers, etc.). The last item was a mid-project scope change, yet they still met the original project timeline. I especially appreciate Don’s thoughtful insights and recommendations (his depth of experience enabled him to provide recommendations that saved me money in materials on this job, improved house safety, and will reduce future angst for upcoming home projects), Christian’s clear communication and work ethic, and Patrick’s polite professionalism. They all worked well together, were timely, listened well, did a significant amount of work with minimal drywall disturbance, and were conscientious about the dust/mess from their work and cleaned up after themselves each day. It was a joy to have them in our home.  Their rates are very reasonable considering the quality of workmanship and customer service; the invoice was reflective of the estimate and mid-project scope change.\nHighly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"mary white-cornell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXB0mFUwd5tYa2BK3qaJ-W22zGx-jOM7ljIbX04c34-TDRmmJM-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This company was extremely easy to work with. Dan came out. I identified the projects we wanted fixed it quickly and correctly and we couldn’t be happier. These are the guys we’re going to call for all of our electrical needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DvaD","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSC7kpZhFSusahv-Rcsjm88XQJQfXyNA2yj9kM5kL4ev2eaZY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Installed 12 LED garage lights. This was a relatively small job so they were able to fit it into their schedule within 48 hours based on  completing another project early. Two electricians arrived on time; they were pleasant, professional, and detail-oriented. I had a general layout planned, but they were able to work out the details on exactly where and how to do the installation. My garage now has great lighting and I can actually see everything we have stuffed away. Excellent job all around!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yelena Dagaev","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJA1ihLu-zQ4omkjQBB2j4KzhN9rF2d_U-7vEdiClpsb5UcxA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Patrick, the Electrician was outstanding.  On time, communicative, knew what the problem was IMMEDIATELY and fixed it to 100% working order.  Steve, the Owner is a pleasure to work with.  I recommend Streamline Electric 100%","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
