ce off our house right when we were trying to get out of town on vacation. Larry showed up on a Sunday and did some really nice, clean, and efficient work to repair that. Even better was that he made some calls to both SDCI and PSE which got us inspected, signed off, and hooked back up in a single day. Incredible service, and all for an extremely reasonable price.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jeff O'Hare","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIayG8JC_McpqGI8TaYpj3h7_HM5mChNnvMMv5OlNSWl92Tw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have worked with Larry's Electric for years for both repair/renovation projects as well as new construction.  His team has always been great to work with.  Very fair and competitive pricing and always honest and good to work with.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sun's Properties Manager","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWunKDFJbMPn6yiRhX0ipVUbsePsRWz8e8WHVHpYkGlTgZ3gq5A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've been working with Larry and his team for a few years now, and they've always come through for us. Their pricing is hard to beat, and they consistently go above and beyond on every job. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve Burnington","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILnAPARgo1t4udL967aN8XTUstNPkdOWrTw3fOUNe5Q8wpJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service and reasonable prices. I was interested in the details of how the repair was done and Larry did an excellent job explaining. Definitely a future customer.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shannon Newman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7BKr78f1li8gHYoX9ffWlxZmp7qdrDxVK_eMWoMJmN4TeP7527Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Larry came out same day to check on the smallest of jobs, which we really appreciated - a broken smoke detector. He was very responsive and knowledgeable, and we look forward to working with him again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roman Migdal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKeqd0Lr_470_WLX4LfpDfc8XXDxLzUuW1ZeUrge28v3SQ_Rw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Im a contractor and have worked with Larrys Electric for many years. They provide great service but most importantly never cut corners so there are no call back. They have done remodels and new construction jobs for me. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
