YlB9nAbrLIx4BX=w446-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=BPTmAZzI6JfzmGLHzk9_nA\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=271.0006\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"102591449815868361896","name":"Emerald City Electric (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102591449815868361896"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Salmon Creek","street":"11645 4th Ave SW","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98146","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Alicia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5h30IcoCnX9URxGWKn3qZvxGCmc_P6SPjxKJjxmW0RIPPJw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Josh was incredibly helpful and professional. We moved into our new home and had some issues with old wiring. Pricing was fair and he got the job done in a timely manner. Can’t recommend enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicolas Meilleur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEHL7f3C3mjF7tsIXKDnW46sh5aO8GHIiD1ciXU7Uj8r2arGds=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kyle, Mark and his crew are super professional and very reasonably priced considering the cost of electrical work these days. I've never had them be anything but super reliable, always on time and work quickly. I've hired them to install panels, wire rooms, etc. They very kindly accommodate any questions, comments or feedback with a great attitude and are just nice folks.\n\nDefinitely would not hesitate to recommend them to anyone, in fact I already have for several family members. Thanks guys and keep up the great work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"William R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLApTd0pGBkfuSxeOKftA0SQYDrzVfxB4cp7PclJG6A_2fGjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kyle and his team rewired my entire house, including a new panel and removed old knob and tube wiring. He got all the necessary city inspections and everything has worked perfectly. He was also the most affordable quote of any other company. I’d hire him again any time and refer him to anyone looking for an electrician.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Diane Robinson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPlHqTEUEv8o5JdS4N-5urJui0V76tR_qlf5U7MPV9XKXvTaBx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kyle and his crew put in an EV charger for us. They were terrific! They came out quickly, noticed important details about the job that our first bid guy missed, and did a clean, fast, great job. And, they were priced reasonably. They will be my go-to guys now!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dani Gamman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZijIV7z-8BEPXaPKEcP0gYbw5aSvw818TJQ4wxPiLGTzVUyi1QQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had the best experience! An outlet in my house had a loose wire, so I had to flip the power off to it which had a bunch of other parts of my house on it so I had no power in like half my house. Josh came out the NEXT DAY and even worked around my schedule. He was super nice \u0026 got the issue solved very quickly. Would definitely use their services again and recommend to others!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ6knBZ60tAnAVLCGbkgRIScCGm20NbRsA650PZRodTtuLu8w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kyle and his crew were fantastic! Good price, good communicators, clear understanding of code. Easy to work with and thoughtful about how things would look after the job was done. I've used 3 different electricians in the past because I've never found anyone I liked enough to use again but I would totally work with Emerald City again on future projects. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Phil Mann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8yBHv8GbhKusvO33hAMoAypEd4jZHqo5ZfJ6uHh_e0k_iGFp5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our realtor set us up with an electrician to swap out our Zinsco panel while we were closing on our house but they were so bad at communicating that we just gave up. Emerald City Electric's estimate was about $2k less than our original. The only delay was waiting for the panel to be delivered. After that, Kyle did a great job installing it and even got a plumber to reroute a pipe that was blocking the panel door at no extra charge. Communication was solid throughout the process and now we won't die in a fire.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Hannon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWMqi2k9QgKjjNlf5hT2J2lAcU9aH5wlGVJSn9ObCMqJKXDt9d=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was great working with Josh. He got my job done, permitted and passed inspection quickly and I’m so happy with my new outlets and expanded electrical panel. I wish I’d called Josh years ago. He made it easy for me.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
