ogleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiCoFNr6GXb0X1DVCgxysdGgNhRFLa2yOIGA0Ivhm6SKg7gP3i=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an EV charger installed by them and didn't have any issues. The install location was far from the breaker, but they were able to do it in a few hours. They were efficient and professional.\n\nGot many different quotes for this install and their pricing was very fair.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"TC LO","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKAQCFctfRNTxOXkVh3qPYebnzXnTq6RP54SyOiTt885Gm8vg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Troy who came to provide the price quote was very knowledgeable and even took the time to share extra information with me. Later, I scheduled a project for outlet replacements and light installation. The technicians, Kadin and his colleague, completed the job efficiently and with great quality. I’ll definitely call them again for my next project.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pamela Kivi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXO8ENNvgSOzf6q4ou_CEgEzvc8DYhsHYoNYqKfCs8di1JlXTQcUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This morning around 4am woke up due to being cold. Attempted to reset circuit went to AI which listed a couple of nearby reliable electricians. Left a message at 'In Charge Home Electric' to see if they could fit me into their schedule. It was past 8:00am so we scheduled for 10:00. Troy arrived and diagnosed the problem, fixed it, educated me on how to prevent further problems and I'm writing this review at 10:40.\nI had overloaded the circuit with a portable heater and electric blanket. The plug in was fried and if not for the circuit breaker I would have woke up to flames or not woking up at all, along with my neighbors since we live in a multi-family home.\nTo say I am grateful is an incredible understatement and we will be getting all of our electrical work done by this company.\nI highly recommend 'In Charge Home Electric' for 