trical service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"quang ngo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKfO_gon9XQm0F65I-qwej32BaPkNCfHJFxSo7qqbCBmeMh3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I reached out via their website looking for a quote for EV charger installation. They were very quick to respond! I appreciated the prompt response very much because I called around couple other companies before that and nobody was getting back to me! He gave me a ballpark estimate over some pictures of panel and the distance in my garage that I sent, and I really liked the price, so I decided to hire them right away! The owner even gave great recommendation of what charger to buy and gave me some rebate info too! They came out, did a flawless job! I'm very happy and satisfied w the whole process! They are my #1 electricians to go to in the future, no doubt! I actually recommended them to several of my friends already! Contact them and you won't be disappointed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dick Harsin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIR8svAdbfYHNVgWJUIN6gH9F1MsHiGfl4yzua5Rydn8z5Aew=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They came out to do an upgrade on the panel at my house and did a great job! I called the previous day to make an appointment and they were able to come out the next day (I called around and no one else could fit me in!). Price was very fair and they even helped change out an old GFCI outlet for free- just for safety! Very prompt, responsible and professional! 5 stars for their service! Give these guys a try and you won't regret!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"sudhanshu shukla","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1LXVRlnvnfgQANQcTOlydYtwWBOVybrYNFhMy6L5_50LC33E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a first-time homebuyer, navigating the various elements of home improvement can be daunting, especially when it comes to electrical work. However, hiring Sergey from 206 Electric was one of the best decisions I've made during this process. From the very beginning, Sergey demonstrated exceptional professionalism and a clear understanding of my needs.\n\nI required a range of electrical work, including the installation of ceiling lights, outdoor holiday lighting, a dimmer switch, and a power socket for my car charger. Sergey took the time to discuss my specific requirements, offering knowledgeable guidance on the best solutions that were both effective and cost-efficient. His expertise in the field was evident, and I felt confident in his recommendations.\n\nWhat truly impressed me was Sergey’s commitment to ensuring every aspect of the project was covered. He handled everything from the initial planning to obtaining the necessary inspection permits. This level of thoroughness eased my stress significantly, as I knew I was in capable hands.\n\nDuring the installation, Sergey’s crew displayed remarkable skill and attention to detail. They were not only efficient but also took the time to explain what they were doing at each step, ensuring that I understood the process. The team was respectful of my home, maintaining a clean workspace and promptly addressing any questions or concerns I had.\n\nAfter the installation, Sergey diligently followed up to ensure everything met the inspector's requirements. His proactive approach in addressing any call-outs from the inspector reflected his dedication to quality and customer satisfaction. It was clear that he genuinely cares about his clients and their homes.\n\nSince then, I have recommended Sergey to all my friends who require electrical work, and each one has had similar positive experiences. He has been super responsive to their needs, making him a go-to electrician in my circle.\n\nOverall, I am extremely satisfied with the electrical work provided by Sergey and his team at 206 Electric. The combination of quality workmanship, excellent communication, and a customer-focused approach truly sets them apart. If you're looking for a reliable and skilled electrician that can tackle both small and large projects with ease, I wholeheartedly recommend Sergey. Thank you, Sergey, for making my first home-buying experience a positive one!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3AJb62--oaSWkcOw6jjD2wSP0fmt2RsruWW0WsvEUakc_Mais_OFXXcFFX4cOxcQhQIbdxj4OEc-NvIN1b9ZASlpXKWOpktuML3U3Km7oNeMXDzB3VattavzaMnIZOo12612egwg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2uY1neuYhBEq_wOQV3qVfTGclzhL8NGc-rYIhZuKQ9NgXxEVRZjXx1ixD2V2upuKOY_kiPE5We8hP4S4WIV2jW7cBAbGT8kn5g0CTRaLHpba8fx8MYrO5rYcTrxT7cYP4v4dsY=k-no"],"When":"2024-12-18"},{"Name":"Matthew Chase","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXdAdUlUwxuWBJn9XNUV7wuScENmQP5WkhmiA4OpiueRWHLtBnpA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"206 and Serge were so professional and very cost-effective. It was a pleasure working with them. They were on time and very responsive.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
