cian from around the way for any future needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Morrison","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXhgzgl-8dm9ee7nP-KUbla1R5TFvXLKEsLzz8TKvHYfuS6A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Scott was a life saver - He installed all the wiring for my new garage/ADU build. He was knowledgeable, detail-oriented, and extremely helpful. He brought ideas that I hadn't even considered. I was impressed with his professionalism and insight. He continuously went above and beyond my expectations and stuck to the bid even when unexpected things popped up. I highly recommend him and will definitely be using him again. He deserves more than 5 stars.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jillian Mochnick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMdvF9ogjVlg2hT8SoQmivT-No2DmhyzgF1A5Fp2zcbtA4FRfssQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Scott offered to come by to give me some advice on some electrical work and offered a variety of options and it was clear he wasn’t trying to sell me on something I didn’t end up needing! When the time comes I’ll definitely reach out to him for help. Appreciate the kindness and integrity.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Geoff Miller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXg9aIbT_GNCvDzmhVfkf7DQNQaL9__c2-vKvBWhqaxbDEJaTWA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Scott is the best. He installed a sub-panel in my garage for EV charging as well as other large power tools. He's on time, on budget, and great to talk to. He will be doing all my electrical work from here on out. 10 stars if I could.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jacob Wood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBINHD2Dindc9E1YGm_sc1cuZUPJnAaJInPsqsBZeKyj1j-A8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Scott is the electrician you want to hire! He was incredibly helpful and informative on the phone even before we officially booked him. When it came to the actual job of moving an overhead light fixture, it turned out to be much more challenging than anticipated, but we are really happy with the end result. He honored the original quote despite the unexpected difficulties. To top it off, he even vacuumed up the area after all the drilling, which was a huge plus!  Highly recommend Scott for any electrical work you need. He's knowledgeable, professional, and goes the extra mile!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jon Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWe7OGQ_ydLub_eo7DpKKABbCmr0Vx5JSOfqbgJ6_czLkeEQo5HvA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recommend Scott. I called and discussed my issue with him. He showed up right after his other job and resolved my issue. I will continue to work with Scott. Reliable, local and knowledgeable.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
