ure":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWxKms8yMHG0Xd5YPUJlyatVheXrR5U6fkstd2bJlNaNhhQg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brian from Live Wire Electric was excellent. He quickly figured out what was causing the problem and explained everything clearly. The repair was done fast and very professionally. Overall a very pleasant experience. I would definitely highly recommend their service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Myrna Casciola","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLPzBPNu9ecfqDVzGXXLFRAQDKH0sd0yfm1laXbF2zwjIJ0EA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was very lucky to have had Live Wire  come to the house and work out a plan to take care of my electrical problem.  Very professional, but very low key to feel comfortable and trusting. Forgive me, I cannot remember the names, one was  Tony just starting out. The other have been in the business several years, I feel very happy to know they will be the two I can count on.\nThank you\nM. Casciola","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Farley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTzBeBdU7Jg8Y-u5oZx1IBAgFZ1F0VN8kLuVyYE--iNjRODpGJ-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Professional, friendly, and fair. Darwin handled our electrical panel upgrade, outlet relocation, and preparations under the kitchen (including crawlspace work) to get everything ready for our new oven installation during the remodel. Everything was done right, and he was a pleasure to have in the house. 5 stars—would definitely use again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeff King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxjHfmcXzhleoSkzmaatDUaf80u3UdVHnftuAvYatzqwhrxA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brian and the folks at LiveWire Electric were fantastic to work with. They saved me from an electrical house fire, I'm not kidding (see photo). Brian himself did the service call. He carved time out for me in his already full day. We're very grateful for him. Thanks, Brian!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2AbA-Y7MYq-fZRuCFL4GlD-VfnBLD_w77dGpTEPocA-QdNK6mGFxLr0qFVfKuEWrOC1l0tg4WKUcYVKDZZpG7KqE1jkk5vZDMjUpdmvStoJXOtPsmjcWcLmc0xxyrVuJVe8Z-xnZvW2NwS=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-13"},{"Name":"Kyung Min Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwQba5zJ3i_dL-AKhp4YxaT1yvz5rK2ke8CNmbx4KSd5oMfdzC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I NEVER write reviews… but I HAD to for this!!!\n\nBrian was AMAZING!!! What could’ve been a stressful situation turned out to be something so simple, but he still took his time, explained everything clearly, and even checked our ENTIRE house to make sure everything was safe!!!\n\nAnd the biggest thing — his honesty!!! He didn’t charge us for something he absolutely could have!!! That kind of integrity is SO rare these days!!!\n\nYou can genuinely feel that he cares about people, not just the job!!!\n\nIf you have ANY electrical issues, don’t even think twice — just go with this company!!!\n\nBrian, THANK YOU again!!! We truly appreciate you!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aristotle Vedant","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKP-Y6xeoDA9ry_h3NA8eRjEN2j-njnWmSo3u0I6O6F5-6FcY0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Darwin came on time for the free estimate housecall. From the get-go, he was able to win my trust and confidence through a quick assessment of my needs, a thorough review of the setup in my apartment and devising innovative solutions to my needs. I was extremely impressed by his knowledge, customer friendly focus and ability to explain and breakdown the numbers behind the estimate. I will recommend their services to anyone who is looking for a hassle free, quality and expert work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah RM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQWRYQzJMnx39xX3nIM31riOYWMiCbc5yIgc9wULL9kPKjZRM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Live Wire always provides top notch customer service, quick responses, reliable and honest work. Everything from their booking process to arrival \u0026 job completion is seamless. They do a great job of keeping you up to date on all expected costs and estimates so nothing comes as a surprise. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1mc4SWZqOF37BUtKeWsLc-3KiurXNes8q9QqZ2REoWiFo-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredibly professional and thoughtful help. They were immediately responsive and made my project work. Very transparent pricing and excellent customer service from people who know what they are doing. The owner Brian came out to work on one issue and then took the time to troubleshoot all the other problems I was having and questions I had. I signed up for the membership they offer because I want them to come and do additional work. They made the schedule work for me and the unique demands of my project. I’ve worked with other electricians and they are my new go to. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
