h=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"101501626816584833005","name":"Keithly Electric Co (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101501626816584833005"},"complete_address":{"borough":"South Park","street":"827 S Director St","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98108","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true},{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"April Bettinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWidOWwgWNW_IcABYMQpNvfE7xD3USKUIfP7_4mwCvKqZDW218t=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"**Exceptional Partnership Spanning Two Decades**\n\nI am pleased to provide this review for Keithly Electric Co based on our extensive working relationship. As Owner \u0026 Founder of Nip Tuck Remodeling, we have maintained a business partnership with Keithly Electric for over 15 years, and my personal working relationship with them extends beyond 20 years.\n\nThroughout this extended partnership, Keithly Electric Co has consistently demonstrated the highest standards of professionalism and reliability. They have proven to be far more than just a service provider – they are a true partner in our business operations. Their responsiveness is unmatched; whether we're facing complex electrical challenges or unique project requirements, their team approaches each situation with expertise and creative problem-solving abilities.\n\nWhat sets Keithly Electric apart is their commitment to collaboration. They don't simply execute tasks but actively engage in finding innovative solutions to meet our specific project needs. This collaborative approach has been invaluable in delivering exceptional results for our clients.\n\nTheir warranty support and after-service care deserve special recognition. Without exception, every time we have reached out for assistance or warranty service, they have responded immediately and resolved issues promptly. This level of dependability has given us complete confidence in recommending their services and has been instrumental in maintaining our own reputation for quality work.\n\nAfter two decades of partnership, I can confidently recommend Keithly Electric Co to any contractor or business seeking reliable, innovative, and responsive electrical services. They have earned our trust through consistent excellence and have proven themselves to be an indispensable partner in our success.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2YQDE3XePnvPnXYrTpHWrTJ46wd4Aw3o1UuWE1e4jerDE8LQyLyshrnIFcn3WT8gGMA1IMhMOt8cNijaUlMs9JtTtJRTNxZL3WLUtY5ISjzVVAzv-7z8_0CiLGt_FR9hpN_vuUYqDZf35T=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2jz1AfnTSjdOIuElbXhLxCZIa6g5EHxrmLtZxsjEeLk-DG5VDMIxhfFmgYXHGZ1XeJ_BD0ZnJn9nznYaerUD2n8LoX8W-IO0jVbcFL9RzxbGP3CFDNF8ezNpW2r9Ma_hzXCeZct_KI1_1g=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2kn5IyRdwoECsPcmdfgWQJPvvIReCLx4V_MrqZR2QJOahOrAlwc0xevC-QtatPGAL143AbV9bjRLV2PO6KWz1z3QSvR5Q5dHgffuOw7mXQTiG89Pb6OUlvjMpVBgDjCUZsqKJZ8dY67FE=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-5"},{"Name":"Janice \u0026 Larry Miura","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIthurRtJ0mtjBg6fi10_ToMVNWsxwNesD4QSqasgwn9MVKVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We moved into our house about 6 years ago.  The home inspection revealed that we had a Federal Pacific Electric Panel which had been discontinued due to the breakers overheating and leading to a fires.  We finally got around to replacing it and chose Keithly Electric to do the big job.  Their bid was very reasonable.  The project manager met with us and explained in detail what would have to happen.  After that it was a seamless installation.  Great communication with us.  The workers were here on time every day.  They worked efficiently and neatly.  No mess was left behind.  We're glad we finally got it done and don't have to worry anymore.  We highly recommend this company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kellie Blair","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTYBokB-tEAygdAo2Y-KFrsfsW3SLgg0G4uc2e_o8nlUW_VtU8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hired Keithly to update some electrical on my 80 year old house.  Their team was so knowledgeable and helpful.  Will be hiring them in the future for other house projects.  Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jason Roberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrYZ8dk-qKHmGf6xwx0iuerH5uNErY8Ge01SjI9mhS5BsnxXvG7A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We’ve had Keithly out several times now and they are consistently amazing! They upgraded our panel to a 200 amp service, installed some outdoor outlets, rewired and replaced outdated lighting, and most recently installed a breaker for our generator. Their electricians are skilled, professional, and above all personable. I cannot recommend them highly enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Loyer-Drew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwGyxHFUwJy_LLrFEIT-mKYSIywD38pje-L3Dn7hF39kwjHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had Keithly upgrade my home's electrical panel to 200 amps.  I got estimates for this project from two other companies, and Keithly's bid was comparable to the lower of the other two.  The Residential Project Manager at Keithly was really responsive to my questions and was easy to communicate with via email, which I appreciate.  They were able to do the panel upgrade within approximately three weeks of me deciding to move forward with the project.  The electrician and apprentice who actually did the panel upgrade showed up on time, were pleasant to interact with, explained everything that they needed to do, answered all my questions, and completed their work on schedule.  There were no issues at all during the inspection process, and I haven't had any issues with my home's electrical system.  I recently had a heat pump installed, and the electrician (not from Keithly) who was part of that installation team remarked that installation of both the meter and the panel (both done by Keithly) had been done especially well, and that he encounters a lot of panel/meter upgrades that have been done poorly.  So, I had a great experience with Keithly, and it was nice to have someone knowledgeable confirm that they did really quality work.  I would definitely recommend Keithly to someone who needs to upgrade their home's electrical panel.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joseph Meek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAT_A8tPxCTZDp7uOGxmGJtjSZDMJ2d1IsR0puhLAo-0vAHw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Keithly electric was the only place that responded promptly and treated me well. I had tried to contact over 7 electricians prior and I was entirely baffled how I could not find a business willing to give me the time of day since my project was not massive. Eventually I reached out to a good client and asked for their recommendation, Jim from Keithly was the name and he sure is prompt and attentive. I had the work scheduled that week and completed in a super professional and timely manner. Andrii who came out and did my install was all smiles and information, he provided multiple options for the install and explained the differences so I could make an educated decision. The work is flawless and he left my garage clean, he even vacuumed up any drywall dust on the ground! really impressed overall, could not recommend more or provide higher praise.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Carnagey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAEBEl3UvsWHouWL-wNH9PT4JwvenbcKt2sqMrg6Dc-HAFkZLs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience with the company. Technician Jay came out for the inspection and bid. Jim in the office got me the bid the next day and we scheduled the work out for the next week. Jay arrived first thing in the morning to replace my whole panel and install a generator hook up. He was very fast and efficient, and walked me through the process of hooking up my generator. Great company to work with and will use again in the future!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anna Cronin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU24IVPmK60B4su2Epa7BJPPXt6-tESolRX47hUee6V8uHyv3xz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Such a frustrating customer service experience. I had previously used Keithly and was happy with the quality of work and the technicians. However, the last two times I have tried to get a bid I've had a terrible experience. Most recently, I contacted them for a semi-emergency job. Their service model is that a customer service rep takes your information and then a project manager returns your call. This leaves the customer without ANY information about when a technician is available and whether it is possible to be seen quickly. It took four days for the project manager to even return my call so that I could find out when they are available. All the while, there is absolutely no electricity in half my home and a possible live wire in the wall.\n\nOut of the other four companies I called, Keithly was the only one with this model. The other businesses I spoke with were able to quote wait times and schedules. I finally booked an appointment with someone else, since I was able to talk to a scheduler right away.\n\nI will not be using Keithly in the future. I have some big needs in my home, and I have no desire to be placed in the black hole waiting for someone to get around to calling me back.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
