,"Rating":5,"Description":"Carroll Electric is one of the most reliable electrical contractors in Washington. I’ve worked with their team on several electrical projects since the beginning and they’ve consistently delivered quality work with fast turnaround times. Their electricians show up on time, communicate clearly, and get the job done right the first time.\n\nWhether it’s troubleshooting, installing circuits, or handling full-service upgrades, they bring professionalism and solid workmanship every time. The crew isn’t just there to clock in! They’re efficient, respectful, and work with a level of care that’s getting harder to find.\n\nEven on more complex installs, Carroll Electric brings experience and accountability to the table. If you need a trustworthy licensed electrician for residential or light commercial work, this is a company that takes pride in doing things the RIGHT way.\n\nI HIGHLY recommend to anyone looking for dependable electrical service in the greater Seattle area.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1b-oaqVsxpHEnMGCYiZzGPJBy0lPrd5PYRWblyXXdqLlyJGGD7PUxSefVXLCrMsx_AeIUAJ4yrD7Dq_gGsn9-ATrIrvgL2OsRoj6_Gwg9f3sPOkkY9BnILnrkDJBT5vAv_ScKVPoMJ6TRl=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3vUry0QO1C21rLiZlAIe6j4yX1bC80IEOyQq9cjdsFz6n3FaXztL72amHV07vspvFhTl1ikgnF6PtwDeWl05iRwXQHXJsSoEG_uSt_h5gPp7_BzIXxjawlYEejqWkY_VU2f3XjGYcF5VVo=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3OzcEsLeNtY7wflZk9G0tKbilSlzcrTKVrYREifE7rlvMlUnakrl0uqwp452ZIfu7OW8lwbb8k4lcFgi2pEvSPsfiWADFW6dg4Dh2UKB4CIULI-CfVDZYKtWcZrQKjIlervDtlTa-sgDYm=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Zihogkh4zruYfNOcQOKYKLNOmJH7t40xzTZeX3pJ4Ik6KshPqmMCHomZL-3CQXz8k9mRDw0Wx9dH1sA6QzMzzIhIhaQkTU9YdWZoGgBd_dLxjZjRSPCLld6XKn5ElBPy9yZYZVtJbDTe0=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-12"},{"Name":"Brandon Vanderley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIodlE-Njnx1_opUAuipvtGvRbDAg0QKEhRh62EjHY6WM7inQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I are very impressed with the service from Carroll electric. I can honestly say they are hands down the best electric company I have ever worked with. We have called them for various projects in the past and will continue to use them for anything needed in the future. They have exceeded my expectations in every area. Carroll Electric always has the situation handled swiftly and with minimal disruption. It’s comforting to know that we’re always in good hands.\n\nFor our most recent project Cameron was incredibly professional and helpful, and didn’t leave a mess behind like some electricians we’ve hired in the past. Carroll Electric has always been a fantastic provider, and I can’t recommend them highly enough. I’m confident you’ll be just as impressed with their top-tier service as we have been. Keep up the great work Cameron, and Carroll Electric!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIb_wV0_xpAQCITTRPPJJDbhUxt5sKDzcltxikDRimWW0YMUc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cameron Carroll of Carroll Electric was great to work with. I contacted him the day before, and he arrived the very next day to fix a broken basement light switch. He was punctual, worked quickly, and replaced the old switch with a new switch and plate cover at a very reasonable cost. Everything works perfectly now. I would highly recommend Carroll Electric.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vladimir K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5Zwczwr0EeyCFeuywdj6VH0uxhcGDHX4t-mYceEsMgp2Xjw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cameron and his team did a great job on our place. They handled electrical work (outlets/switches), installed light fixtures, and took care of the bathroom fan/ducting work. Communication was solid and the work was done well 👍","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy Bergsieker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJrWRvrew3mIMJ8oH8Byz9qGqlcWuiLOX18MPtosH20BF0J0A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I contacted Carroll Electric to help me repair two outlets that were not working and to replace my thermostat. They replaced both outlets and installed the thermostat in an hour. All are working perfectly. Will definitely hire them again the next time I need electrical work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ali B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5zyWwyJLb-pWTa3VaC2J2-QQkGlSJUGt-7TmnspumYnYbSA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was so impressed with Cameron and his work.  He fitted me in ahead of schedule which was extremely helpful.  He explained how he was going to go about the work. got on with it very quickly.  He was very polite and delightful to work with and I am so grateful for his help.  I recommend him highly.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
