ps://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgpu42Jvn9mM0Izz0rvGhJFcnSkWwaesUI1OPlb_8QboPMMHHU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Outstanding service! We had a wonderful experience with this company. They were punctual and professional from start to finish. The end result was aesthetically pleasing and functional. Highly recommend this team!\n\nWe needed an outlet added for an electric fireplace we’re installing. They asked all the right questions in the initial consultation, and confirmed the tech specs of our fireplace before the install. Both the owner and install team were respectful, affable, and very knowledgeable. Will definitely have them back to update our panel and add more outlets in our garage.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2ZmxEGyh0QN2L7Kak0F5KGrbVYTfIgHySCCJWEBXHq47sP3TWJ54MH8PfutTO7tmxWPR2bqXRhymAQ8tj42-_Xb4ii6fjo1cBExtoLobG6FFFxX_zKdRzpLupMqDbLd1Gwk_jx5-u7dko=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1ZwNfVHijy0sZWo1PSfPxudgGbRlUnOYSPm0kjXRvPF_z9c2dVikz9l8oDjv7Jb4ManaUw3trf38k2gsbzPnjipW23NGsDgJCrF-Xflz3bW4k0PtQF7BbZv19LN-tnmuwA6dOAiryFR_GM=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2T1KnDD8FcVwaOHp7cs9OMqHOXAOhc4CWGfuT3KuHNXrxGzOp9WDIaI7msexxnvfu9He49B1dby_mf1j0B-DH-IvfMN3dJpVl6OVFnYcUYebuM_W-r5CpgEU11dUv5WJctzAQONIwp3XFZ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1sSc_GkhpK8ldSWobIEB3tR2SeWJ4MscSAmPj4n9PhLrLqmAdWKE4xiWw-PpukK0-myIbs_1mpCYIfmEJOtOzEkk7j_Naat041yWze2dxGqHPPweP7099_sG6sLWGHI-d5N8tsIgdShOQb=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-30"},{"Name":"Courtney B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcPg43Dc67EqyJEy5_fCMoOJJy43aufO6_WHOTUS2X-3Ry3A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alex, Bo, John, and the rest of the Renew team that helped with our electrical upgrade were outstanding professionals. Scheduling was very easy and they were punctual. They diagnosed our issue quickly and provided multiple options during the initial service appointment. Their recommendations were reasonable and trustworthy. They had all hands on deck for installation making quick work of a big job. We now have a safe fully updated electric system (guaranteed for life) thanks to their work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Guillermo Santiago","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDqJITizaqEbKWUZ7DH_2G0G_McHNuNhyptZahymuACe473w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I contacted Renew for two projects: installing new circuits and power outlets in each bathroom of my two‑story home, and relocating existing light fixtures plus installing three new pendant lights in the kitchen.\nFrom the initial call through the first visit, Alex was fantastic—clear communication, responsive, and right on schedule. After reviewing my requirements, he conducted a detailed walkthrough of the house, clearly explained the plan, and provided a clear and transparent quote. The cost breakdown was straightforward with no hidden or surprise charges, which I really appreciated.\nOnce we agreed on the scope and pricing, scheduling the work was a breeze. On the first day, the installation crew arrived exactly on time. The lead, Alex (2), introduced himself and the rest of the crew, reviewed the project details with me, and walked through the house again to confirm everything. He clearly explained the installation process, identified access points needed for the work, and then got started.\nThe second day, focused on the kitchen work, was just as smooth. The crew was professional, well organized, and worked efficiently without cutting corners. They took great care to protect the areas they worked in and left everything clean when they were done. The quality and cleanliness of the work exceeded my expectations.\nOverall, my experience with Renew was an easy A+. Excellent communication, professionalism, technical knowledge, and transparency from start to finish. I would absolutely recommend them and would not hesitate to use them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ash","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL3NujQVGR5q6Snrp8b7sjsLtucRs_5y97CMskUQLMnPIHTTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The team at Renew Electric was fantastic from start to finish. Both Alex—the technician who provided the estimate—and Alex, who handled the installation, were professional, courteous, and easy to work with. They provided a competitive bid with zero upsell pressure and took the time to explain everything clearly. The interlock kit installation, complete with all the necessary features, was completed flawlessly. Before leaving, they made sure all our questions were answered and even walked us through the generator hookup process, covering all the important dos and don’ts. Outstanding service all around. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Luke Higgins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9GwKcTmvZegWaXsbhT3kOmATPLXYUsWAJQbbnLU8CrzaizLA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I filled out a request for a panel upgrade online to get some quotes. I thought I needed an upgrade because my main breaker kept flipping. John mentioned that didn't sound right and offered to do an inspection instead for $150. Went with that since the cost be rolled into any additional work needed. They ended up finding the main wire was loose and tightened it. I decided to upgrade anyways. Went from 125 amps to 200 and it costed ~$7k. It wasn't the cheapest offer I got but Renew had 3x the 5 star reviews as the lowest bid. They did a great job and new panel looks great! Now I can run the central A/C, dryer, microwave, and anything else no problem. Very happy with the improvement 😁","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn045Ov8tHzHAbnUe9UEz-iNYlMnBxLyLTlhfSEliVF7lXe3FLEhsqSYeLkdRz9On_ayjc-EsqwhDKrH6KWHxDh8HAAk-wcf9PpFKwSQJa0er4A5pz7bs8tzvSB27CeSEF1IugB-b3nAYJM=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1YLg2S02rIGQ8m2JbOutDk46-tA2Jd-vki66IrQEsuXeEmMPxmJCobmo_MPBHfiYnpaau80ctngOGssm0mcTeWd13fy85GkoxJdwSAW2u-V96u3R2194CjyaPPGlR7ScxkZ9vD8tN3pHHe=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-8"},{"Name":"Patti Reed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgcOeqozs-FyJtH1_8h82xJmH84RQTvK13w6gmLNOKLin7yg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We asked Alex from Renew Electric to give us an estimate for adding an outdoor 30 amp plug, wiring and new transfer switch for a portable generator. During his visit he also checked our main panel for any connections that were done poorly or not done to current code. Our main panel has had many alterations  over 26 years so we weren't surprised when he found wiring issues that were concerning. He asked thoughtful questions,  carefully considering the electrical needs and issues of our property.\nWe met with him over an impressive and well put together Zoom call where he went over three very thorough estimates from the most comprehensive to the more basic, based on our more immediate needs.\nWe were impressed by Alex's thoroughness, friendly demeanor and professionalism during the whole process. He's also a super nice guy, someone we would be most happy to work with and would certainly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robert Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIGrjtDHH4MM7UU9UGXoHP5oFKqLXFMW4zWv4UPUhrXYRl0XA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great company to work with.   Alex and the rest of the team were very professional.  They did a complete re-wire of an older rental home that I own after identifying many dangerous aspects of the older wiring.  I was aware that the old wiring had some problems but not of the extent.  I first contacted Renew Electric when an emergency developed when a heater wiring started smoking behind the wall and they was very prompt in coming out to fix this urgent problem.  They did such an excellent job with that initial project that when it became apparent that the house needed  even more extensive work I did not even bother to get other estimates.   Perhaps (or perhaps not) I could have gotten a cheaper price quote but I knew that I would not have had the same degree of confidence in the quality of the work.   Thank You Alex and team for providing me with the peace of mind of knowing that my tenants are safe.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nancy Tom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyUav_bMYF9upsJIDwo22dLgOpPJVfhwGiP6QyKpn9L24c7MA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Detail-oriented crew focused on getting the job done properly. Friendly, polite, easy to work with. I appreciated their timeliness, or a text telling me if they might be late.\nWe had new lighting in our family room installed, wiring hooked up to our breaker box and the exterior meter, which was dangling, brought up to code and firmly affixed to the wall. Also changed out a couple of dimmer switches and changed the smoke alarm.\nWould call again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3UtGStwIhxhNZoP5vacdBBjXvWsdYdd_cSx7UHshYdK4Nnz9_IvYfhybuXa3eL3CjuqM1nd9bWZZhQ934aEeWN8r3T2HQmAcGvp4JOuowg-C7n5cXgX0mzH93X1X-b3z4DLa_yrY1gCk8=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2U9sqYNO1ajv3bL6P6-ZMI3Bo5NSk2vvZiVY_IrepL1sGEtF-qZq0F7euDit_YHAOqL5-7zjuwcJ6NUB5ieMYhPTvGnYFPKHuTkGkppuy99PVB-zxcSWS6fmA137Nq_Xo_TksmEC9FMIel=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3LC_WX1WDdXSjTocFd-ocOhbqmK4BLzx78ZOBzY_2oi0T-y35W966zaMZYecFfLToU705cvBmkvJFJizvzBHvPHYqsUnmkASi5WuOgmHSnkeBSBgfnGHZcs5vVBZSEXOjWG7mKauFtCNJi=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-14"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
