yond — especially Donald, who put in an incredible amount of time and care. Their workmanship was impeccable.\n\nThey took the time to talk with us about what we wanted, clearly explained what needed to happen, and offered excellent suggestions and recommendations along the way. We felt informed and confident throughout the entire process.\n\nI will always recommend Rock Electric — and Donald and Ace specifically — to anyone who needs electrical work done.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zev Chonoles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNiBf8xw4uyfBcuoXLvgNKIaW5Z8C0Pct8ZZPXO1VMTyuNQSjTzg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've used Rock Electric for two big projects so far - two years ago they ran Ethernet through the entire house, and just this week they installed a battery backup system for us. Both times, everyone involved was very professional, happy to explain all the options and details of how things work, and communicative about what the status of the project was throughout the process. And both times, the end result has been extremely high quality!\n\nBig shoutout to the team from this most recent project - Aaron, Angel, Ben, Jacob, and Ace, thanks for your great work!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2xo6m72XMO4FXsmwKCULP1087RP_AOnTe6Kd-S5pJB1yV_VyH3L7qrJFnCqpl5_mbBqzpS032GU2cB6lTcnWsmf6K-ZI7wdCk6vrIOps05x1ZTWcS9aUOxn2ghIRWw7Xm9JUEHHMUpjemf=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1DKwePS0iBN5X4Njb1Rdv3y_sKBf7W3KL-oc7QSRiVYX5JSD4w7jW3jjjzjjuRRflSd6vLZr3mAJtb7CBPLGdWxA1rOjd4yzLRFduzRIrRdyGIkybH3gO3IGhMumADoy7oyewwTGAH3CI=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1JuA80b1wPi2ThIGomAGWP-DMPDJCOkZQT5jKMGIIrHepUhW92788_Uwt7DNvTmxwQfSRvpMJNBGlLqgmCOVmeJefpx-HpQMbinTaRNGdnrE2HesfAmCWbAGwCSFHm5hXhIOFDiyL1088=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-13"},{"Name":"Linda Jednaszewski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDntv8hdyAmvOuCa8519dfWJZ93u2uGUBZ8POz2NcKSW5cilU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rock Electric was recommended to me by my landscaper, who also trusts them for his projects.  They’re truly professional at every step from the proposal all the way through the installation. I love how organized Rock Electric is.  They are excellent with communication, have everything down to a science, always follow through, and do excellent work above all.  I would hire them for every electrical job I ever have and would recommend them without any hesitation.  I value excellence in execution and this is THE company for the level of excellence I rarely see anywhere else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pedro Santos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvIC2QAkyGy57W-Rx4BxQq2n0BGdnS6-u6AcSInVHxUiLDYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was our first time using Rock Electric for a home project and we couldn’t be happier with the results. Ace and Angel were our technicians and they were amazing. They were professional, on-time, friendly, communicative, and extremely efficient. We had to update the wiring and outlet for our new range and were unaware of how big of a project it would end up being. Ace and Angel were patient and explained the process and put us at ease. The project was done way faster than we thought it would be and the end product was exceeded our expectations. We will definitely be using Rock Electric for any future projects and will hopefully have Ace and Angel as our technicians again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeff M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXmHOOBKRWDh_RAGzxfrQFIy1gWJSqmohTydd3ZZbKgdBl_F3c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m really impressed with the work done by Brad Wood at Rock Electric, LLC. He did an outstanding job installing the latest EcoFlow Smart Panel 3. The installation was clean, and he demonstrated excellent knowledge throughout the process. It’s already paid off, we had immediate backup power during an outage. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa Berglund","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwm03wl3943Unj9CLnNf_osaj8ThyNdbqYQdRS2ASs5J8QNjt6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Don and Ace from Rock Electric are the best! They tackled a big electrical project at my beach house — replacing a very old panel,  adding outlets, and installing a heater on the deck. Everything was done with professionalism and care. Don and Ace kept me informed every step of the way and made the whole process feel easy. The quality of their work is excellent; it’s clear Don and Ace take real pride in what they do. I’d call Rock Electric in a heartbeat and highly recommend them to anyone needing electrical work done right!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Penelope Goldman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrWWo610a0yzaZBALbKB1iK7VTj5l1ym_BghVjlaUzNSizeS0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Needed a sub-panel upgraded and several new outlets installed. The electrician was punctual, knowledgeable, and tidied up all his work. He also identified and fixed an old, unsafe wiring connection in my panel at no extra charge. Trustworthy and skilled Needed a sub-panel upgraded and several new outlets installed. The electrician was punctual, knowledgeable, and tidied up all his work. He also identified and fixed an old, unsafe wiring connection in my panel at no extra charge. Trustworthy and skilled","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
