a stepped in to handle my big electrical renovation and got everything up and running. They are professional, know their stuff, pay close attention to detail, and really care about their work. I highly recommend their services to anyone needing electrical work. 10 out of 10!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Drew Zavala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKTTG385uNUBZNevsyWrPmfFpLihT_rDZYr1vnovkWqn02XA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've relied on these electricians for all my projects in Burien. Our house is over a century old, and they've been fantastic at updating the old knob and tube wiring. They've also handled things like mounting a TV on the wall, swapping out old light fixtures, and even installing a cool closet light that turns on when you open the door. No electrical job has been too challenging for them—they always find a solution and get the job done right. Highly recommend their professional and friendly service!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
