to the walls for access points in which they only were only willing to cover half the cost. To add to the issue regarding this company. When my wife \u0026 I went to their office to drop off a certificate check for the job. Once we arrived at their office they had on display a \"BLM\" flag in the window which my wife and I found to be very offensive do to the ideology this company supports. To top things of when the final inspection was done the company had a female employee there when the inspector was there as a distraction which led to the job being signed off on with an exposed live 220 volt with which was a potential danger for fire, humans or our dogs. This company needs to seriously rethink it's business practices.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
