ions","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Billy Dang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlvVhZa0IyYa7uXHpzh29JOdxot5-gJY15p2y18VeKibuyQtY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Aloha Electric is amazing. Robert is the best electrician in the business. Excellent service from start to finish. This is my third time calling Aloha Electric for my electrical needs. Robert is always professional, courteous, and took the time to explain everything clearly. The work was completed with precision and high-quality craftsmanship. He arrived on time, kept everything clean, and ensured everything was working perfectly before leaving. I highly recommend Robert with Aloha Electric for anyone needing reliable electrical work! Look for his truck! No job too small! Hawaiin vibes included!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn037mIHrZtN3aEi1vt3JJZditVyGUNNi3yWFQxpBUnqlO8ukkaKvmJe2I4GPxr04rHhz7fIS7_WJFaTsMXhzivt5thowYWlbdC3rcO6_-oIKCH25FVbjc5tIHgIYeTZJH6Dr51j0JLbdH2I=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-12"},{"Name":"Tanee Manohchompoo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLrFRs_qZRrk23XjBIfvcVZ3FogEZPT7n5JAMrygeKJVoNuafw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Robert Cullen was very courteous, punctual, and knowledgeable. His honesty, along with his good attitude was why I decided to go with Aloha Electric to install an interlock circuit breaker and exterior inlet box.\n\nAt the start, Robert gave me a fair estimate after price-checking with a few other companies. He was thorough with his work and took it upon himself to repair some messy electrical wiring in the electrical panel without being asked. The work didn't take long and he made sure any mess made was cleaned.\n\nBeing a tradesman in the commercial construction field myself, I've come across many workers, and I appreciate workers who take pride in what they do.  Robert definitely checks all the boxes, and I definitely will call on him again for future electrical work. Thank you!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn26-fCF02dfYuNf7bqeTyeK9WgP5SoCsHN7z1IQGPVFMla5T6BC2GvoUbiFMy01G1tFoh8c-g5zOxUsPlhsaZ_2T62zJM6-FO8XyzWeUL3vJgygz28NnEBXAE1j_AVuxRM0pN2a=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0seOawDxx1cmXaksPKxfBb-XN7Ely50ltpZ53y-gmS8hsLhG3k0OigqP5IX6iGsuDiV0Qo_l5KbN4iagdU5Fd6Ln2vGSLDllFfYrg2axMHPQABnOswkxTB8XNiQFA5QhzjnmT3=k-no"],"When":"2025-1-29"},{"Name":"John Cowan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAsnLrq7BmvrTy7vmb_0-6Y_uJ-BsKXPCE0NtoR0A926DVfcoD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Robert was friendly, professional and clear  with his estimate and explanations. The work was done quickly and excellently. Would definitely use Aloha Electric again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cody Conder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_Vzd2jlz7CfjNR0XMgpI5Enf4AVphKCKjiFG6qI1OIfodCT6uNw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you’re looking for a skilled electrician, look no further!\n\nAfter going through three extended power outages in our area in the last year, we were done. It was time for a backup solution. We decided to go with an Ecoflow Delta Pro Ultra battery backup and Smart Home Panel 2. I’m a relatively handy person and have done some basic electrical work myself in the past, but there was no way I felt comfortable trying to install an electrical panel on my own!\n\nWe reached out to multiple companies for estimates to install the panel and move our critical circuits over. Robert came by our house to discuss the project, along with other electrical projects we had in mind for the future. Given the amount of work required to install the panel and the fact that the Ecoflow panel is a brand new product on the market, we found his quote to be fair and competitive with other quotes we got. We also found Robert to be an extremely friendly and professional person, someone we would be happy to work with.\n\nPrior to the installation, Robert took the time to research our setup, even going so far as to reach out to Ecoflow for clarification on certain installation requirements. By installation day, he knew the panel inside and out.\n\nThe installation of our new panel went flawlessly! It’s clear that Robert is a person who takes great pride in his work. He left the electrical panels looking pristine and left no messes for us to clean up. We couldn’t be happier with the work he performed! We would strongly recommend him to anyone needing electrical work done in their home, and we would definitely hire him for our future electrical projects!\n\nUpdate 10/22/2024: I know that some folks like a \"follow up\" to reviews whenever possible, so here you go!\n\nIt's been several months and about 3 or 4 extended power outages (lasting anywhere from 2 to 8 hours) since we had this panel installed. Everything still functions flawlessly! We honestly couldn't be happier with the results and the quality of the installation now that it's been put to the test multiple times.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn17aQh-clq-qBOHcAsXWIFOKM8ljse1Clge0UakyXAr0qb1jPcw5spkOfNT0IDQGdULxVvKJN-ZJgwRUksuc3ykPYc2zuJgXaLHG5g-54Sc_eXrsYbkBLUIQE-Au4O5EHQeIJ_A=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn34e5NNMjXQ_XWKXC9O5u2OBTIqW9nLq6Y_MNRydec51aCM8e7JUgnrfD9y1m8mOHjvHr_cyg_crT_vfMSQ2SNCJ9fm8xidfRKVNwAsSEnWXXihJmV1KsWM4CqDT_F3ycZSACN7Hg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0i8vzB-_f3RgPSMUV4kaZikuWzsIO-mtnBzz3sheDUSvU-eI5KV26TRXrdMA-VZQ2Ozvie2PBh-ObbIS0YzOYTZO991PDDG5_WoVyID9SxOb5sCIDBCl5glKTDM2EGoX1FRLdc=k-no"],"When":"2024-2-15"},{"Name":"Christopher Batalon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJYPx9xPmhtJ51mzGPuPg7uUIBPmalwtWCyAItY5rFHroXTOA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Robert, really embodies the \"aloha spirit\" always showing kindness, compassion, and the willingness to serve in a very respectful manner. I have done consults with Aloha Electric LLC twice and both times Robert not only answered my questions, but offered me economical cost alternatives and gave solid advice on how to handle my electrical needs. I would highly recommend Aloha Electric LLC to my family and friends (which I have done in the past) and will continue to do so. Appreciate you Robert!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Billy Dang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWm5NmzHhUtVBsNHh-HT6zOhJNdUDkLTOq7JMoQR190h44bjkc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Aloha Electric is amazing!\nGreat customer service and professional. Robert is awesome! I needed a 240v outlet installed for a electric car charger. Robert did a amazing job running the outlet from the breaker box across the garage to where I needed it. Install was fast and professional. Works perfect! Will definitely be calling Aloha Electric for all my electrical needs from now on.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1MDY5damHRmBr13mn2M0ZZSe9TKG_GXby_vcmv6rxCRTAUN5QyesLBu1ZrOfAgHvLU8QPHyLbQjEFiI_7hr5cimec8I-0s1aGNSWRCUJi_945RTCEVCvHqTGWOGxPlcxJ2ruU=k-no"],"When":"2023-12-2"},{"Name":"Glenn Wood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtC4RakeR0O5GnKf_EBAgIhdBJMuTs3wAWnoihgkLLgqLCOA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Robert is very professional to work with!  Prompt, efficient and does excellent work!  Highly recommend and we will use him again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKpG5iGTuxCZGINktiXbH4f3GVZBBYr3i_c6YZfergJEQebcg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hired Robert/aloha to do a small job to replace some exterior lights. He did excellent job and went above and beyond to make sure that the lights looked aesthetically perfect. He literally got his hands dirty!!!   He has always been very responsive and dependable. He shows up when he says he’s going to.  And he charges a reasonable rate.\nI am getting ready to do a second story addition  and remodel, and Robert is doing all electrical work. His quote was straightforward and all inclusive. Last year when I reached out about putting in a temp elec heaters, ,he told me that it wouldn’t be cost-effective. So instead of just taking the job and making money, he guided me to a better option. He earned my trust!\n\nI’ve worked with lots of different subcontractors and to be honest it’s been really hard to find a good electrician.  I really think I finally found one in Robert!!!  I look forward to leaving a follow up review after our large project is completed!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
