tric! De Andre made scheduling and communication easy right from the beginning. He is incredibly knowledgeable and efficient with his work. His quotes are very reasonable. We had a dedicated 20 amp circuit installed and DeAndre was able to troubleshoot and resolve a separate issue right after. We will definitely be reaching out to Crimson City Electric in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jon Freeman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmU0XiHq03WRDuERdIYOfUFOkrEx4pplRc7DIToCV8tEXSgbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Did a wonderful job on my main panel upgrade and AC sub! My old panel was ancient and completely packed. Got a new larger panel, clean “pro” wiring, with better distribution and even room for dual EV charging. My AC sub was also great and even my HVAC tech liked how they did it. Thanks guys!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"lynne nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5OEo2ArPCYw8udDRQXuv4WOnUiXe4yRGTvwrlYk6rz_GSTGD6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a sudden mysterious circuit shorting situation. De Andre responded quickly to my website request, got out to my house quickly, and identified and solved my problem quickly and efficiently. He communicated clearly, had a reasonable rate, and I really appreciated his skill and expertise!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ethan Broga","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGK-Sdl5HcgTeEfQTOwJ6LI8lttHYYW_K11IQLvcGjalWlVUMI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"De Andre is great to work with.  Communicates effectively and easy to work with.  Does the job well and within the quoted time frame and cost specification.  Will call him first for any future electrical needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andres Martinez-Alegria","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ2qer7zWmrusMdg9JLAo_vYRmYfYTOkXQx797_6TtovU6lzG0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Descripti