een an invaluable, reliable, and amazing resource to us since we bought our current 1950s-era house, with all its decades of previous owner \"remuddling,\" as well as original era wiring and outlets. We've called on them numerous times to do everything from installing exterior power for a hot tub, stand-alone shed, 50-amp RV hookup, and electric car charger to diagnosing a broken dishwasher and installing interior and exterior light fixtures and smoke detectors. They have been responsive, efficient, skilled, knowledgeable, and compassionate throughout. I can't think of anyone, in any field, I would recommend more highly.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3bMgztUDTKheiSyXJDxJsZSeaTBBhoB-vsVWlk0eHrBMY3wpvj8dJF8htKEjS2yDMydltvsVkITLSKdlflbYnhk7pygsFF_3nV6vNrGuTiiLHeIdG4QbMrMVxstm9hjujHt3NxcQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Lm6IBVv_zR2UPHnv6CgSaSgT1XKCZ003vSpyOpJqPnkOK8dfLHHjeFtWqf7156xmstOHvRYqvpzaFGfbxjPNwM00jfH5gQkyxcMFAsN0XWahWX1q-zGFgW1U8Z4QlcLVIzwgg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ekyIniSDiNebzZCMiMUAna7jXiegrA2YNUxiMXLCA-mjwUyJeW5wsn8x1K-AEJGgB4MKGkQpBVHukeROqxdMZy1-FtU8kntoFDQrAs5guwW-PcCl7CIqnsKVFfj3rXjfh_yXXnA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0FeSSdM6u9mYbwhnMapz7VIrd8QwNN8S9Ny8cDi9NQY5F5eRsicK52INvQxveASkCXoGOgFDvBByuKkX1EI7iBHhDrDyb7pCSJUuOshSEx0Fs1pAC9r8kP04u4QwAHdfGX9n3r=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3nz98zrqCA0CN0-qeFeARJGrUV2CrH93HbpTOFf_xs_mLJFCJjXvnX25_CDp3_CZfjBBTq_fDf1-SQuHpNpHB22NL1BDpJpyFJM_KfEqRHMhgXTQuSAk-R3IJKBdpQmQEJaz8UQA=k-no"],"When":"2021-3-19"},{"Name":"Mark Baker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpf_-zq49g8C4D_bI3AeYpdo7aDuHP94MVy626EkM_ikJA1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Deb at Veritas Electric is just fantastic! I recently bought a condo and Deb rewired the newly renovated laundry room, updated the switch in the electric panel, next, she installed my smart thermostats, and then reset all the heaters. She and her crew are great to work with - polite, friendly, professional, and very neat in their work. For all three jobs, Deb provided an easy to understand estimate, arrived on time, and completed the projects on time and within budget. And, explained everything thoroughly. Highly recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lucian Hardner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7H5MTSam0vZEMxt-bpABm64DyKNoz5-C7OWplOLHZHNh4-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Deb and her crew (I've had the joy to work with her, Kari, and Arlene) will exceed expectations from start to finish on any project you have. I needed an electrician to upgrade my breaker box and I'm very glad I found Veritas - I've already had them back for a smaller project and will look no further for any electrical work I need done. Everyone is so nice \u0026 professional, and they think of everything! Truly a white glove experience that made me feel in safe and good hands. 🥰","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dawn Zedonis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_EbX-8ab5empzVKbFOAMrOxtArmfkHrEICV2K1-Aa47PRIfE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Deb and her team at Veritas Electric are rockstars. Deb's estimate was clear and competitive. The work that they did was impeccable.\n\nThey swapped out light fixtures, replaced old outlets, installed new exterior outlets, and replaced recalled breakers that I didn't even know were lurking in my panel. Deb walked me through how to get compensated for the recalled breakers and generated extra invoices for me in order to streamline that process.\n\nI'll only use Veritas Electric moving forward -- it really doesn't get any better than this.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"betina blaine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZx_50JnT6PqblTz_TLZmtDqORInboGDNZik4HsVOZGJRyqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Deb and her team are phenomenal to work with. We are so glad to have found Veritas. We almost gave up on our kiln shed when a competitor’s estimate came back sky high for a plan that would have required extensive digging and subsequent repair. Deb quickly came up with a creative solution that saved us a lot of time, extra work, and money. They also installed an electric car charging station for us. She and her crew were professional and delightful, and communication was great. Inspection passed easily first time. We are so happy to support this fantastic all women business. We would not hesitate to hire Veritas again. Great work Deb!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian McCoy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0styqoRyXlEQNadrakGUiyLRZRhM8Z-9CPoY2-f8B8Bo4Zm3P=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Deb and her team at Veritas Electric did great work on our home. We had a room in our home re-wired with new can lights. A bunch of old ungrounded outlets and switches in a couple other rooms were also updated. They also installed an ethernet port into the wall to help clean up the computer wires a bit.\n\nDeb was professional and knowledgeable, and just a delight to work with. The estimates were on the money, and the price was reasonable. I'll definitely look to Veritas for future electric needs. They're good at what they do and they know the value of good customer service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jane McKinley-Chinn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7sFEWY7GxVBuUKuE7HNAtWL5kT7IZLfl1W3GFCjxzOHPVkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As the Owner/Electrician/Estimator of Veritas Electric, Deb is friendly, reliable, knowledgeable, and her extensive experience is reflected in the high quality of her work.\n\nShe scheduled us with very reasonable appointment times for estimates and actual installation.\n\nWe had bought two replacement roof-high external dusk-Dawn light fixtures for an Electrician to install.  They were the wrong fit.  Deb helped us by recommending two suitable options of long-term outdoor LED dusk-dawn light fixtures.\n\nWe recommend Veritas Electric highly.\n\nJane \u0026 Mel Chinn","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Genya Shimkin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvKbA_W2rMpQlf14ppfPvQAk3nzN2aLP-17DxROcJijh8iMgqM9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Veritas is our go-to electrician. Deb is fantastic- communicative, professional, and organized. She recently rewired our upstairs and added multiple new outlets. She walked us through everything, answered all of our questions, and finished multiple days ahead of schedule. We will definitely work with her again!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
