":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Sonya Perales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVg8TEq8TOhW43Q-U6vFXdOPVeOAaRfpuFrUqMBcBM_-EEYy2kz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Here from out of town, went on a wild goose chase for charging stations that don’t exist. Local recommended this spot. Charged my car to 50% in less than 15 minutes and I was at 2%. I’m going back to this areas ihop just so I can charge at this station again after my kids concert.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Woody Sellers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXj9mzJvZwV_JG4-KbjQvlb9tck2VuCRwNH8YNPrC4gP-pEIUsgHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It's a \"Hyper-Fast\" charger (up to 350 kW) but I'm maxing out around 65 kW on my 2025 Equinox EV. Not sure why I'm not getting more.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3xp1zaJGKOqWalVia_HAj5vFD26OuRJsFZSQQbRazKdDkzGPoUy2pmH1NgcHdS7rcFyzkGuSZO0mP6mQ_s4iBR-KQzTLeS77I3CxSWrnQG_xSyoZgLzkIpPqsr-5C2yLKNcAajHvk6hLVg=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-7"},{"Name":"Arian Kulp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHYtIkD6-mLdvkRSx90Tr3EPZDQQOzW6APxSckixOuUmhMn4A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Every time I go to this charging station it's always full. They need to add more chargers. More often than not. There's also at least one that says unable to charge. This time. Somebody parked a zip car across one of the chargers. I know that's not EA's fault but it's still upsetting and it was the last straw. I hope that they choose to expand this station soon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mustafa Hafeez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSFcI9Um-z8gUPcceC0inW3sXPDXx7Ud7-1MJHvzhnpbYdVlKk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"As others have said, a separate parking fee is not required while you charge. Also there are NO Chademo chargers here, only CCS. So make sure your car is compatible. The Zip Cars do tend to take up the spots very frequently, and the parking fee for the lot if you want to park is an absolute joke.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zac","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxA9rwz2NRnYrv7NBib5qI-BaMWHvDGNU_D66M4Bootuam8OXU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hit 191kW for awhile.  There is no cost for parking while charging your car.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3pBzOah3XFrXGXuxp6NX-m1aW5YfneF-D-X-cDHRnu-QYV3hGfeMF7bPUPBkFhE_SOmmVkTP6wG6RWI1V6NdLsxCNZpP38jlLbtSIOx0KtuuLsVR-aHCFuZWvvAUp9auMqZj0=k-no"],"When":"2025-5-21"},{"Name":"Christopher Harrell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKM_JnC54oOzqONhgFSbMSOKZkwE-M1jN-Or9AUrNOGyVFTig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The Zipcar attendant here hogs up all four chargers to charge the company cars. It’s so frustrating and this happens every time I’m there. Zipcar has a lot next to these chargers and the guy here takes up the chargers all the time","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chad Gamache","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfxTQvGIa3gFwu9BTChfKXxDMQZ6jR004jrR3onS6aqymQQ5Tx=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"You don't have to pay separately to park as others have claimed, but the lot layout is horrible to getting into/out of chargers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pamela Love","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUkKubdgc_pWA7clALbN01Y8nlh1GWfG5UONdf30Vy0WaZ7pFCGw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"2 stations of 4 are not operating.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
