l as fixing a few other problems, all for a reasonable price.  Five stars for speed, attention to detail, and solving a lot of small problems that have bothered me for a long time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bob Jacobs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxyGR8nEi8SJANNAv1cutPHzaU8R-ZCiZceBOYDohnppu5YQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Curtis and Dan are simply the best.  I've been a car guy for decades, and I rarely see their combination of expertise, very fair pricing and superb customer service.  Was referred to Acme by my mechanic for a computer-related electrical problem.  Acme solved the problem quickly, fairly and with remarkable expertise.  The world of car repair needs more Acme!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aishwarya Nair-Driscoll","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDMT3kagMJCkYLlzvxgzQaZpelsPXpMwwIelaZaFTGjxjPV9Q7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"really great service, and nicer to know that i was supporting a small biz! i showed up 45 minutes before closing because i was concerned of a wiring issue with my headlights and the team took a quick look and immediately addressed the issue, going so far as driving up the street to find a replacement bulb. as they were wrapping up i asked about a potential brake issue and they took a look and gave me a rough estimate for what it would cost— such quick service and i’m looking forward to bringing my car back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Philip Curry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2qrNqjRqBV0JchUed3g-UaG6lLHbYcgcPpbn0LXPkkStDCVgO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience with Acme. Brought my 04 suburban here for various issues and they handled all of them well and efficiently.\nCurtis is a solid guy, very knowledgeable and transparent. Communication was prompt and accurate and courteous. He’s been at it 43 years, he knows what’s up!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name"