,"Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Caroline Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-ZZEqgl_iuL_XsLOVjV8C4oHx4izykVZnpE3Q-r6KlezYsg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Norman and his team were fantastic. Everything was finished quickly and affordably. They found some additional issues while doing the electrical work and were able to fit us in to get those resolved ASAP as well. We are delighted with the work they did!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S Mo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOw6pPoty6N6q3UczyzBdQYtW0yOLzoVi1g9VXw82xC1W-Kg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a wonderful company! I got 2 bids from two different companies. Norman's was by far the more reasonable one.  He showed up on time with 2 other people and they didn't stop working the whole time.  They did exactly what we asked for with excellent communication and problem solving. I unequivocally would recommend this team. We had a 20amp outlet put in for a bidet, moved a light switch from one side of the room to the other and had an outlet replaced. I learned a bit about what was happening because my questions were very welcomed. I always like to add for single folks out there about the safety vibe and I'd feel safe having this team come to my home if I was alone. Respectful, efficient and reasonable folks. A+","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"JMW","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIimA-9iFbd8E8JmGK8LCSdWg7KISkokzrN9s38R4CIzlUe0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I will trust no other for electrical services! It started with a simply inquiry last month about new lighting and switches, which led to new heaters and thermostats. One month later, through some miracle and flexibility on the part of Norman and his team, everything is done! They're very knowledgeable, efficient, and genuinely good people. Call for a quote - you won't be disappointed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Danni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbkK9CfhkBsRg7fzNU521ygLP9MQY-T3l2bE_oN0S5A7goEUXd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Norman was very quick to make a stop to evaluate an emergency situation due to catastrophic incident. He had someone out early the next day to take care of the needed things so I could proceed with the clean up of my house.\n\nUpdate:They did beautiful work on my total home restoration after a catastrophic event made my home unlivable. Their work is detailed with great  care and they did everything to get back into my home as quickly as possible. They value quality of work. I highly recommend working with Norman and his team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpijNS5fP1Llm-sDX6GG_KZCU6NwHfd7oejY1rWYtNCALpQg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an electrical emergency on a Saturday when we discovered an old panel behind our kitchen cabinets had live wires which tripped a breaker and turned off the lights to half the house. I called Estarik and Norman happened to be in the area and arrived at the house within 10 minutes. Not only did they quickly diagnose and fix the issue, but they came back the next day to replace the old panel with junction boxes, installed a new panel outside, and brought everything up to code. Highly recommend, will be using them for all my future projects","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matthew Yglesias","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxR7tky6UUrRVCR-bxkTqSGavz_TjKU99zdRSAV0ChaGYceIaa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nathen came in and assessed our problem, came up with a solution and came up with the best price out of 3 bids. Very happy with his professionalism and service. We will definitely hire him again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy Portacci","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSHZzVrhO4i6PZpJ6JdHMjRUgdXMsWhQ5v