ated electrical panel. Eugene came out and did a great job with the upgrade. He explained everything fully and truly cares about the quality of his work. It was clear to me he was very knowledgable about his craft.\nHis prices are very competitive. This solved our issues with tripping breakers and we haven't had a single problem since the upgrade. I would highly recommend Reign City Electric for your electrical needs.\nDoug J.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jason Abner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLblgj9CdKt56Dgcr-h1WqRukS6uI4KoVqRuinMBDW7NjvcJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Reign City Electric was awesome and I will definitely use them again for future electrical work. Eugene is very knowledgeable and responsive with communications. The electrician that came out was on time, assess the situation and quickly installed a new circuit breaker. I was very pleased with the work and service provided.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelly Rang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6fsuiFpjjMzlPgCJOQ2LwehssVWRfU5NTnWXkMM5l_0wTWjDn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I contacted Reign City to install a light fixture in an awkward spot in my house (in the middle of a hallway with a 13-ft ceiling). They were very responsive and came over quickly to install the fixture. They did a great job and I couldn't be happier. I would definitely recommend using Reign City if you need an electrician in the Seattle area.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Parsons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnFMWno9zw4GmevJqDxm6Brk81oeoWPzmrCbkUpMzauyU8XRHM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They did a great job. Fast, affordable and efficient. I'm happy with my new fixture. Totally worth having someone help who knew what they were doing in a tall hard to reach area.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2eNERQ50OPjOXJxYOwi_xs_-R9v25d